{"tid":263161,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] AMD Ryzen 喺VirtualBox 行舊OS時出現黑畫面嘅解決方法","createTime":"2017-05-29T18:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T14:41:15.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48a6709e87944a81066092b4d97823845194339f","tid":263161,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T18:36:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NCTnH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNCTnH.png&h=81566f2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forums.virtualbox.org/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=82323\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforums.virtualbox.org%2Fviewtopic.php%3Ff%3D1%26t%3D82323&d=XHnYWkiZIwOO3qOg8qC8sb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=55a1010a\" target=\"_blank\">https://forums.virtualbox.org/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=82323</a><br />\n<br />\n原來改cpuid就解決到呢個問題 (淨係試咗XP係work，Win7或以上唔洗搞都可以正常行到，其他舊OS唔多清楚)<br />\n<br />\nCMD (run as administrator)<br />\n<br />\ncd C:\\Program Files\\Oracle\\VirtualBox<br />\n<br />\nVBoxManage modifyvm &quot;XXXXXX&quot; --cpuidset 1 00800f11 00000800 56d8220b 078bfbfd<br />\n<br />\nXXXXXX = Your VM<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div>"},{"pid":"8bde81fc1a431fbd570bd8f0ac607165ddb1bacb","tid":263161,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T01:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce908bd7a218c515990811d7e74d8fe8b6b6f123","tid":263161,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T14:41:15.000Z","msg":"我用唔到systemcare<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}